Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.37,0:01:29.24,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,give me an answer
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.86,0:01:35.65,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,不器用でぎこちないほど
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.07,0:01:38.65,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,愛しく始まるの？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.95,0:01:40.76,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,give me an answer
